  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK62">
<l>eḻupiṟappun tīyavai tīṇṭā paḻipiṟaṅkāp</l>
<l>paṇpuṭai makkaṭ peṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In all seven births, evils will not touch you if you obtain</l>
<l>children of virtues that reproach cannot approach.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
